    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤏 <strong>Got Your Nose!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this nose-talgic journey, you play as <strong>Sniffer</strong>, a runny nose with snotty legs and toes. <strong>Sneeze, sniff, and snot</strong> through the strange sewers of <strong>Scentropolis</strong> to restore order one smell at a time.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👃 <strong>A Nose Like No Other</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this <strong>quirky</strong> adventure, <strong>oxygen is your lifeline</strong> and <strong>snot is your greatest weapon</strong>. Zoom through with snot, sniff flowers for hidden powers, and <strong>use every breath to survive</strong> a sewer full of bizarre critters and silly surprises.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/aa9c473c6f657cd0eb435b8f81c1ae7a.avif?t=1770279052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras_big/aa9c473c6f657cd0eb435b8f81c1ae7a.avif?t=1770279052 width=800 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/f5c840bd2654db3c3561bf7d6ba89030.poster.avif?t=1770279052\" width=810 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/f5c840bd2654db3c3561bf7d6ba89030.webm?t=1770279052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/f5c840bd2654db3c3561bf7d6ba89030.mp4?t=1770279052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💨 Your <strong>breath</strong> is more than air, it's your<strong> fuel.</strong> Manage <strong>oxygen</strong> carefully and <strong>sneeze</strong> your way through deep sewer tunnels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🌟 <strong>Master</strong> the art of <strong>breathing</strong> by overcoming challenges one <strong>inhale and exhale</strong> at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌻 Sniff out <strong>flowers and scents</strong> that restore air, unlock <strong>special powers</strong>, or reveal <strong>hidden pathways.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/7f92b4d98744a1da76561e9d15766713.avif?t=1770279052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras_big/7f92b4d98744a1da76561e9d15766713.avif?t=1770279052 width=800 height=225 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/cc08bbccfc4a83d54dd6f7e6a00c9314.poster.avif?t=1770279052\" width=810 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/cc08bbccfc4a83d54dd6f7e6a00c9314.webm?t=1770279052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/cc08bbccfc4a83d54dd6f7e6a00c9314.mp4?t=1770279052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🫧 <strong>Experience snot-powered platforming!</strong> Bounce, stick, and glide through levels using <strong>Sniffer’s snotty abilities.</strong> Every obstacle becomes a playground.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/46a86622a4f322aeb10a47f870362b46.avif?t=1770279052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras_big/46a86622a4f322aeb10a47f870362b46.avif?t=1770279052 width=800 height=225 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐌 Meet the oddball residents of <strong>Scentropolis</strong>, from sewer critters in trouble to silly allies with stories of their own.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌆 <strong>Explore scent-sational levels</strong> filled with humor, secrets, and the occasional suspicious smell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >💡 <strong>Smells Like Home</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nasal Nomad: Sniffer’s Delight</strong> is designed for anyone who loves a good twist. Easy to pick up for younger players, but with enough challenge and secrets to keep seasoned platformer fans hooked.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Family Friendly Fun</strong> - Lighthearted humor, colorful worlds, and quirky characters make this platformer perfect for players of all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👃💨 <strong>Smell Ya' Later</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Do you have the nose for it?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Wishlist Nasal Nomad: Sniffer’s Delight today</strong> and prepare to sniff, bounce, and be part of the smelliest adventure on <strong>Steam</strong>. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: right\"><i><strong>“Every sneeze echoes a tale. Bless you!</strong></i><br><strong>~ Sniffer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras/b216285ba49bf03f7a1391252874419e.avif?t=1770279052\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135980/extras_big/b216285ba49bf03f7a1391252874419e.avif?t=1770279052 width=800 height=111 /></span></p>",
